	   <tr><td colspan=2>Druids have a superior taunt compared to the sucky melee taunt, and here's how to execute it.<br><br>1. Buff your tanks RIGHT AFTER THE THE MOB IS PULLED.<br><br>2. Heal your tanks AS SOON AS THEY LOSE HEALTH.<br><br>3. Cast a DoT RIGHT AWAY.<br><br>4. Cast snare and start nuking UNTIL YOU CAN'T NUKE ANYMORE.<br><br>Now sit back, check for any clerics in the zone, and watch your tanks try to save you.<br>&nbsp;<br>Ganerin, level 39 Wood Elf Druid<br>Vinaelil, level 25 Dark Elf Warrior<br><br>Officer of the Rune of Flames guild on the Veeshan Server</td></tr>
