	   <tr><td colspan=2>You only lose faction if you take a faction hit when killing the mob. If you see no faction hit, as you won't for unnamed bears and wolves, then you don't have to worry about it. As the previous poster said, other npc's will however attack sometimes. Centaurs in South Karana will attack you if you kill an elephant in their vicinity. But you can kill all the centaurs you want and take no faction hit.<br><br>So, just watch for faction messages.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
