	   <tr><td colspan=2>At level 26, Highkeep is the place to be.&nbsp;&nbsp;Everfrost mammoths have a life span of about...I don't know the fraction of a second is too small.  Rangers often hunt them and their track is superior, and they run faster. So, port to the cozy corner of the Steamfont Mountains and into Ak'Anon.  Ask for directions to the lone mechanic next to the merchant, and use the root-snare-DOT-nuke method to kill him.  Drops small ringmail and FS weapons.<br>&nbsp;<br>Ganerin, level 39 Wood Elf Druid<br>Vinaelil, level 25 Dark Elf Warrior<br><br>Officer of the Rune of Flames guild on the Veeshan Server</td></tr>
